content.text: Hi there!
Hey! How's it going?
Doing great! I just started a blog on parenting.
Oh, that's awesome! I'm a nurse, so I have a lot of experience in that area.
Oh, that's great! I'm sure you have a lot of good advice to share.
Yeah, I do. I've been a nurse for 10 years now, so I've seen a lot of things.
That's a long time! I'm sure you've learned a lot.
I have! I've learned a lot about the human body, and I've also learned a lot about how to care for people.
That's great! I'm sure your patients are lucky to have you.
I hope so! I try my best to help them.
I'm sure you do. So, what made you want to be a nurse?
I always wanted to help people, and I thought being a nurse was the best way to do that.
That's a great reason! I'm sure you're a great nurse.
Thank you! I try my best.
So, what's your favorite part of being a nurse?
My favorite part is getting to help people. I love making a difference in their lives.
That's a great answer! I'm sure your patients appreciate you.
I hope so! I love my job.
That's awesome! I'm sure you're great at it.
Thanks! I try my best.
So, what's your least favorite part of being a nurse?
My least favorite part is dealing with the bureaucracy
